snippet.title: QC: Doom Edition. Blood Run and Covenant. Release Trailer
snippet.description:
It's almost time. Less than 24 hrs from now, QCDE will be released, once and for all along with our custom levels, among which you might see a couple known ones.

We'll be hosting an online event right when the mod releases. We (the team) will be playing for as long as our bodies allow us, with anyone that's around. We'll be playing deathmatch and possibly other modes. Make sure you join our Discord server, since that's where we'll be updating the status of the event aswell as participating in voice chat.

Discord Link:
https://discord.gg/XzD2TdV




Music is
"Augmented" by Michael Markie, for QCDE

Check out his Channel for awesome music and awesome Quake Champions videos
https://www.youtube.com/c/MarkieMusic

You can also acquire most of the music from the album here:
https://markiemusic.bandcamp.com/album/augmented
